ğŸ’¼ Scalability & Growth Potential

The backend is designed with scalability in mind, using modular architecture, clean code separation, and cloud-ready components.
As more restaurants and users join the platform, the system can expand to:

Cloud-hosted microservices

Geo-distributed CDN

High-volume media uploads

Real-time interactions

This structure positions the platform for growth, partnerships, and potential sponsorships as the ecosystem expands and gains traction.

ğŸ”§ Backend Responsibilities

Expose secure REST APIs for all app operations.

Validate JWT tokens for every protected action.

Manage media uploads and CDN-based video streaming.

Handle authentication, authorization, and role-based access.

Execute business logic for both panels.

Provide secure, optimized communication with the database.

Support future upgrades without breaking existing functionality.


